&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Fusion Worldwide&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fusion Worldwide is one of the world&#39;s leading independent distributors of electronic components, with operations across North America, Europe, and Asia. We help engineers, procurement teams, and supply chain leaders at some of the most demanding companies in the world find the components they need — fast, at the right price, and with the quality assurance to back it up.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have invested significantly in building a best-in-class technology stack that gives our buyers and our commercial team a genuine competitive advantage. That stack includes Palantir for data intelligence and buyer cohort analysis, HubSpot as our CRM and marketing automation platform, Amplitude for product analytics, ZoomInfo and Lusha for contact enrichment, GA4 and&amp;nbsp;Algolia&amp;nbsp;for search and web performance, and a proprietary eCommerce platform serving buyers globally.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you own&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You sit at the intersection of marketing, sales, and data intelligence. You own four things:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; The pipeline engine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marketing-sourced and marketing-influenced&amp;nbsp;pipeline is&amp;nbsp;your primary&amp;nbsp;metric. You build the programs — nurture, ABM, re-engagement, post-RFQ follow-up, onboarding — that move buyers from discovered to sales-ready. You do not measure success by&amp;nbsp;sends&amp;nbsp;or open rates. You measure it by pipeline contribution and revenue influence.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Palantir&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;HubSpot activation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the defining opportunity&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;this role. Palantir&#39;s cohort data — commodity search patterns, order history, RFQ timing, account behavior, geographic demand signals — needs to become the input to HubSpot automation that has never existed at Fusion before. You design and build the

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This opportunity is for analytical and self-motivated candidates who can multitask and manage their workload in a fast-paced environment. This candidate will be working with like-minded team members in a vibrant and energetic office environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we can do for you!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide training to give you the knowledge to thrive in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer support through a collaborative, and open environment with proven professionals with decades of expertise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable growth through direct and focused mentorship&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you can do for us:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle and timely process customer orders and enquiry (Import / Export / Trucking)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor the status of orders and liaise with the respective parties to ensure that delivery meets targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proper keeping of the full set of necessary shipping documents and to comply with the company’s processes, and regulatory restrictions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update stock card and prepare weekly stock report to ensure inventories accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interact with 3rd party test houses and logistics provider in day-to-day executions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Involve in warehouse capacity planning, productivity improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate data against audit requests and ensure completeness of data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the Organization Audit Focal prepare for the internal/external audits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to meet tight deadlines and prioritize workloads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other administrative tasks as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we’re looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 2-5 years’ experience in a Logistics Coordinator role, also open to candidates with Customer Service experience in 3PL Logistics services providers environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree in Business Administration, Supply Chain Management, Logistics, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient with standard business tools (especially Excel).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to multitask and take on new roles as and when assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work independently and have initiative, good interpersonal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong spoken and written communication skills in English and Chinese to handle overseas internal and external stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Having high attention to details.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cooperatively with others to achieve targets and objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
