&lt;p&gt;Fusion Worldwide is looking for a Test Automation Engineer to join our Singapore team and help ensure the quality and reliability of our RMS platform. This role focuses on validating new features, verifying business workflows, identifying defects early, and working closely with developers, product owners, and business analysts to deliver high-quality software.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manual testing is the primary focus at onboarding — writing and executing test cases, verifying business workflows, and documenting defects with precision. Over time, this role will stand up and grow our Playwright end-to-end test suite, taking increasing ownership of automated regression coverage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate has strong manual testing skills, excellent attention to detail, a disciplined approach to test planning and verification, and hands-on experience with test automation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Can Do for You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer support through a collaborative, and open environment with proven professionals with decades of Warehouse expertise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable growth through direct and focused mentorship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Can Do for Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review requirements, user stories, and acceptance criteria to ensure testability and completeness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and execute test cases covering functional, integration, regression, and edge-case scenarios.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify software changes against business requirements and expected system behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, document, and track defects through resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform exploratory testing to uncover unexpected issues and workflow gaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with developers, product owners, and business analysts throughout the development lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Validate fixes and perform regression testing before releases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain automated end-to-end tests using Playwright.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in improving QA processes, testing standards, and release quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in sprint planning, backlog refinement, and release activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Required Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
