&lt;li&gt;Strong manual testing and defect investigation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of a Bachelor’s Degree in relevant field is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience writing clear and effective test cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of software development lifecycle and Agile methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
